1
00:00:00,810 --> 00:00:03,940
I thought we were done, Director.
Why are you calling?

2
00:00:04,940 --> 00:00:06,480
Even if these are burner phones,

3
00:00:06,750 --> 00:00:11,380
you know how dangerous it is
for us to be talking right now.

4
00:00:11,450 --> 00:00:12,480
We're in huge trouble.

5
00:00:13,150 --> 00:00:18,090
That lawyer, Kang Baek Ho,
took all the shredded ledger documents.

6
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:20,530
What am I supposed to do now?

7
00:00:20,660 --> 00:00:23,360
Calm down. There's no need to panic.

8
00:00:23,430 --> 00:00:27,870
But my embezzlement
and my overuse of the anesthetic...

9
00:00:28,430 --> 00:00:29,670
will all be exposed.

10
00:00:30,670 --> 00:00:32,540
Maybe I should just flee the country now
while I still can.

11
00:00:32,600 --> 00:00:33,610
Are you insane?

12
00:00:33,940 --> 00:00:37,710
The police questioning went fine today.
They think it was an accident.

13
00:00:39,310 --> 00:00:41,380
If you get spooked and try to run,

14
00:00:41,810 --> 00:00:45,480
you might as well be confessing to murder.

15
00:00:46,620 --> 00:00:47,620
Got it.

16
00:00:48,950 --> 00:00:51,160
Tail them without being noticed
and report back to me.

17
00:00:51,360 --> 00:00:54,130
Stop worrying about pointless things
and just stay put.

18
00:00:54,460 --> 00:00:56,330
I'll take care of everything on my end.

19
00:00:58,760 --> 00:01:00,060
Oh Jang Mi. Kang Baek Ho.

20
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:03,100
Those two actually dared to snoop around
the hospital?

21
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:05,040
I can't believe those two.

22
00:01:05,100 --> 00:01:06,870
Chairman Ma won't just sit back
and do nothing either.

23
00:01:07,340 --> 00:01:10,380
I was just told on the phone that
Secretary Kim is on the move.

24
00:01:10,480 --> 00:01:12,910
Even so, we can't have
the hospital director run away now.

25
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:14,580
The moment he runs,

26
00:01:14,950 --> 00:01:18,820
the police will think it was premeditated,
not malpractice.

27
00:01:19,020 --> 00:01:22,520
The most pressing issue is the autopsy.

28
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:23,620
I know.

29
00:01:23,960 --> 00:01:27,430
The fact that the propofol dose was
administered way over the legal limit...

30
00:01:27,930 --> 00:01:29,560
will be brought to light,

31
00:01:29,990 --> 00:01:32,560
along with the illegal drugs
that were found in Seo Rin's system.

32
00:01:33,230 --> 00:01:36,430
How do you intend to stop the autopsy?

33
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:38,740
Don't worry, I have a plan.

34
00:01:40,270 --> 00:01:43,140
Alright, let's head to the funeral.

35
00:01:44,140 --> 00:01:45,540
I should at least see the state...

36
00:01:45,980 --> 00:01:49,880
that brat Oh Jang Mi is in at the funeral
with her own name on it, right?

37
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:54,850
My sweet Tok Hee...

38
00:01:58,620 --> 00:02:00,460
This is all my fault.

39
00:02:00,460 --> 00:02:02,160
Because of me,

40
00:02:02,690 --> 00:02:05,500
my sweet Tok Hee is dead.

41
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:08,600
Mom.

42
00:02:09,930 --> 00:02:12,040
You need to pull yourself together first,
okay?

43
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:15,370
Tok Hee.

44
00:02:15,370 --> 00:02:16,710
My sweet Tok Hee.

45
00:02:18,440 --> 00:02:20,510
I'm so sorry.

46
00:02:20,950 --> 00:02:23,950
I feel like I'm being torn to pieces.

47
00:02:31,060 --> 00:02:32,120
- Mom!
- Ma'am!

48
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,890
- Mom!
- Mom!

49
00:02:33,890 --> 00:02:36,390
- Ma'am, hold on!
- Mom, wait! Try to get up!

50
00:02:38,930 --> 00:02:40,570
Why is she causing a scene
all the way out here?

51
00:02:42,670 --> 00:02:43,900
Ok Hee, Tok Hee.

52
00:02:45,270 --> 00:02:48,540
I'm so sorry you were both born
as my daughters.

53
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:53,510
Yes, Father. It's a healthy baby girl.

54
00:02:53,580 --> 00:02:56,080
- You're not stealing the baby, are you?
- Shut it!

55
00:02:56,150 --> 00:02:58,550
I can't let Chae Hwa Young
take you from me.

56
00:02:58,620 --> 00:03:02,190
Jung Suk Hee heard everything.
Just find her, now!

57
00:03:02,290 --> 00:03:04,820
- Find her! My life depends on it!
- Help me!

58
00:03:04,890 --> 00:03:06,420
- There she is! Let's go!
- Is anybody there?

59
00:03:06,490 --> 00:03:08,660
If we lose her, we're all dead.
Go get her now!

60
00:03:08,730 --> 00:03:10,400
From now on, this baby is mine.

61
00:03:10,830 --> 00:03:12,630
I said she's my baby now!

62
00:03:12,630 --> 00:03:14,030
Die! Just disappear!

63
00:03:14,770 --> 00:03:16,770
Please just spare my baby.

64
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,980
Get rid of them after dark.

65
00:03:24,410 --> 00:03:25,580
Ok Hee, Tok Hee.

66
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:29,650
Live a long and happy life.

67
00:03:31,350 --> 00:03:32,350
Promise me...

68
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,490
you'll live a good life.

69
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:53,500
You witch!

70
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:54,970
You evil monster!

71
00:03:56,810 --> 00:03:57,840
- Mom.
- Ma'am.

72
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:59,340
Ma'am, please...

73
00:04:00,180 --> 00:04:01,250
You...

74
00:04:01,980 --> 00:04:03,820
You killed my daughter.

75
00:04:04,250 --> 00:04:05,920
You killed her!

76
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:09,320
Bring my daughter back, you monster!

77
00:04:09,690 --> 00:04:14,530
I said bring back my daughter,
my poor Tok Hee!

78
00:04:14,590 --> 00:04:15,990
Let go of me!

79
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:20,800
Get her out of here
before I call the police.

80
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:23,430
- What are you doing, Ma Seo Rin?
- Ma Seo Rin?

81
00:04:24,370 --> 00:04:26,070
Why should I listen to you?

82
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:28,710
Right, because you're not a real mother,

83
00:04:28,970 --> 00:04:31,840
you'd never know the heart of a mother
who's lost her child.

84
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:34,210
- What did you just say?
- Chae Hwa Young!

85
00:04:35,910 --> 00:04:38,480
I swear I will rip you to shreds.

86
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:42,020
I'll rip your organs out one by one...

87
00:04:42,250 --> 00:04:46,420
and make you die in agony, Chae Hwa Young!

88
00:04:46,760 --> 00:04:50,830
- Why is she...
- Mom, are you okay?

89
00:04:55,630 --> 00:04:57,000
Tok Hee...

90
00:04:58,070 --> 00:05:00,240
My poor baby.

91
00:05:05,180 --> 00:05:07,910
Bring back my daughter!

92
00:05:08,210 --> 00:05:11,720
Bring back my daughter!

93
00:05:20,190 --> 00:05:21,390
- Ma'am!
- Mom!

94
00:05:21,460 --> 00:05:23,260
- Mom!
- Hey, Tae Pyung! Quickly!

95
00:05:23,590 --> 00:05:25,360
- Mom! What do we do?
- Come on!

96
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:26,700
Mom!

97
00:05:27,230 --> 00:05:28,670
Goodness, that was terrifying.

98
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:31,370
That's what a mother
who's lost her child is like,

99
00:05:31,370 --> 00:05:32,570
even if she's a half-wit.

100
00:05:32,770 --> 00:05:33,870
Doesn't she seem...

101
00:05:34,910 --> 00:05:36,670
like she's come back to her senses now?

102
00:05:37,310 --> 00:05:38,910
No way.

103
00:05:38,910 --> 00:05:39,910
What is this?

104
00:05:41,250 --> 00:05:42,350
Has Jung Suk Hee...

105
00:05:43,650 --> 00:05:45,720
really come to her senses?

106
00:05:55,890 --> 00:05:58,100
Has Jung Suk Hee
really come to her senses?

107
00:05:59,300 --> 00:06:00,600
If she has, what am I going to do?

108
00:06:01,070 --> 00:06:03,940
It'll be a huge problem
if she starts threatening to sue me.

109
00:06:07,610 --> 00:06:08,670
What's the update?

110
00:06:09,070 --> 00:06:11,540
Do you really think Jung Suk Hee
has come to her senses?

111
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:13,510
I didn't notice anything
out of the ordinary.

112
00:06:13,950 --> 00:06:17,150
Don't worry. There's no way
she could recover that easily.

113
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:20,620
Okay, just keep a close eye on her.

114
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,560
Grandpa!

115
00:06:45,910 --> 00:06:47,880
Seo Rin.

116
00:06:49,650 --> 00:06:50,980
Your grandpa...

117
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,720
was too late.

118
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:58,560
I had already found the best hospital...

119
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:01,360
for your facial surgery.

120
00:07:02,490 --> 00:07:06,100
I even had the plane tickets ready.

121
00:07:07,530 --> 00:07:09,930
How could this have happened?

122
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:16,570
Your useless grandfather...

123
00:07:17,910 --> 00:07:19,740
was one step too late.

124
00:07:19,740 --> 00:07:21,850
Seo Rin!

125
00:07:22,450 --> 00:07:25,680
Grandpa.

126
00:07:26,820 --> 00:07:29,150
Grandpa, did you miss me?

127
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:32,820
- Grandfather.
- You little rascal.

128
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:34,690
Seo Rin...

129
00:07:36,290 --> 00:07:41,500
It feels so vivid,
like it was just yesterday.

130
00:07:42,870 --> 00:07:45,840
How could this have happened, my child?

131
00:07:47,710 --> 00:07:48,740
How could I...

132
00:07:49,870 --> 00:07:53,710
How could I possibly let you go?

133
00:07:54,210 --> 00:07:55,380
My sweet girl...

134
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:59,780
Oh, my child.

135
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,350
How could you...

136
00:08:03,090 --> 00:08:07,630
How could you leave
before your old grandfather?

137
00:08:09,390 --> 00:08:10,630
Seo Rin!

138
00:08:14,330 --> 00:08:16,700
Seo Rin!

139
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:18,840
Grandfather,

140
00:08:19,940 --> 00:08:21,440
I'll live for the both of us,

141
00:08:22,670 --> 00:08:24,040
and I'll help you.

142
00:08:27,250 --> 00:08:28,680
What's the story with the hospital?

143
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:31,320
Is Kang Baek Ho still snooping around?

144
00:08:32,220 --> 00:08:34,490
Let him. He won't find anything.

145
00:08:35,050 --> 00:08:36,520
Even if he pieces together
the ledger scraps,

146
00:08:36,990 --> 00:08:39,690
it has nothing to do with Seo Rin's death.

147
00:08:40,660 --> 00:08:42,190
All right, that's a relief.

148
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:45,300
Anyway, what's going on with Jung Suk Hee?

149
00:08:45,930 --> 00:08:47,100
How is she doing now?

150
00:08:47,370 --> 00:08:50,940
Her side dish shop has been closed
ever since the funeral.

151
00:08:51,670 --> 00:08:53,370
It seems she's taking it very hard.

152
00:08:54,940 --> 00:08:57,010
She's at least sane enough
to know her daughter's dead.

153
00:08:57,580 --> 00:09:00,540
She's putting on quite a show.
What a piece of work.

154
00:09:01,350 --> 00:09:02,350
But...

155
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:06,780
Chairman Ma was vowing to make the doctor
who operated on Seo Rin pay.

156
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:09,250
How did you manage to smooth that over?

157
00:09:10,090 --> 00:09:12,660
You even managed to avoid an autopsy.

158
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,900
Throw that bastard doctor
who killed my granddaughter...

159
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:20,330
in jail right now!

160
00:09:21,170 --> 00:09:24,200
How could you not even bother
to properly vet him...

161
00:09:24,370 --> 00:09:26,770
and let her die like that?

162
00:09:26,770 --> 00:09:28,540
This is murder!

163
00:09:30,070 --> 00:09:32,640
I want an autopsy done on Seo Rin.

164
00:09:32,710 --> 00:09:37,420
Father, what Seo Rin took
weren't your typical diet pills.

165
00:09:38,250 --> 00:09:42,520
They were special pills from overseas
with an untraceable narcotic ingredient.

166
00:09:42,990 --> 00:09:45,220
What? Narcotics?

167
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,560
I just found out today myself.

168
00:09:47,990 --> 00:09:52,230
Father, if this goes public,
Seo Rin will be remembered as a criminal.

169
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:54,130
What are you talking about?

170
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:57,370
Why would our innocent Seo Rin
be branded a criminal?

171
00:09:57,440 --> 00:10:00,870
They went ahead with the surgery
because her blood tests came back clean,

172
00:10:01,310 --> 00:10:05,680
but it turns out the drug she was on
was a special kind that is undetectable.

173
00:10:06,210 --> 00:10:07,610
And that's why it was banned.

174
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:09,250
But how could...

175
00:10:09,710 --> 00:10:11,320
she even get a drug like that?

176
00:10:11,450 --> 00:10:14,350
She was so desperate for results
that she sought it out.

177
00:10:14,650 --> 00:10:17,420
If we push for an autopsy
and fight the doctor,

178
00:10:17,690 --> 00:10:21,660
all we'll be doing is advertising
that Dream Group's granddaughter...

179
00:10:21,660 --> 00:10:23,160
took diet pills with narcotics.

180
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:26,530
We must protect Seo Rin's name
before punishing the doctor.

181
00:10:28,270 --> 00:10:30,670
I'm as furious and heartbroken as you are,
but what can we do?

182
00:10:30,900 --> 00:10:33,300
We have to think about
our Seo Rin's honor.

183
00:10:35,610 --> 00:10:36,610
Darn it.

184
00:10:40,980 --> 00:10:42,110
Seo Rin.

185
00:10:43,950 --> 00:10:45,550
My poor girl.

186
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,220
It's because...

187
00:10:48,990 --> 00:10:52,420
I didn't love you enough.
That's why this happened.

188
00:10:54,630 --> 00:10:56,290
I'm so sorry, Seo Rin.

189
00:10:58,630 --> 00:11:00,530
I'm so sorry.

190
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:04,970
Anyway, I'm just glad
it's all been taken care of.

191
00:11:05,870 --> 00:11:07,710
Tell that hospital to shut down quickly.

192
00:11:08,170 --> 00:11:10,110
It'll be a headache
if the police start sniffing around.

193
00:11:10,310 --> 00:11:13,010
Yes. It looks like they're already
in the process of closing down.

194
00:11:13,410 --> 00:11:14,410
Right.

195
00:11:14,780 --> 00:11:17,780
You made sure to erase all traces of us
at the hospital, right?

196
00:11:18,420 --> 00:11:21,620
- I was never at that hospital that day.
- Of course.

197
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:24,590
I've already created a solid alibi for you
using your phone.

198
00:11:25,260 --> 00:11:27,690
I've meticulously checked
and erased any traces...

199
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:31,960
of your visit on the hospital's CCTV
and the cameras in the area.

200
00:11:32,730 --> 00:11:33,830
Good. Excellent.

201
00:11:34,770 --> 00:11:37,170
Now that Jun Ho is
even working in line with me,

202
00:11:38,100 --> 00:11:39,570
I can finally breathe.

203
00:11:46,340 --> 00:11:51,550
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

204
00:12:02,390 --> 00:12:03,630
So, who's next?

205
00:12:05,230 --> 00:12:06,230
What do you mean, "who"?

206
00:12:08,630 --> 00:12:10,400
I know everything about...

207
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:12,900
how you let Seo Rin die.

208
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:15,640
You think I'm the one who let her die?

209
00:12:15,940 --> 00:12:16,970
Aren't you?

210
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:20,110
Using your own biological son...

211
00:12:20,580 --> 00:12:23,380
to send the adopted daughter
you raised for 30 years to her death.

212
00:12:23,850 --> 00:12:25,080
What a twisted display of a mother's love.

213
00:12:26,950 --> 00:12:28,150
You're truly something else.

214
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:31,360
Jun Ho, it's not like that.
Don't misunderstand.

215
00:12:31,420 --> 00:12:32,960
Are you going to deny it to the very end?

216
00:12:35,030 --> 00:12:36,830
It sends shivers down my spine
just thinking about it.

217
00:12:37,860 --> 00:12:41,630
I thought you pushed for Seo Rin's surgery
to win her over to your side.

218
00:12:41,900 --> 00:12:44,030
I thought that was your plan,
and I fell for it completely.

219
00:12:44,900 --> 00:12:47,710
But how could you let the daughter
you raised for 30 years die?

220
00:12:48,140 --> 00:12:50,940
In business,
some circumstances are just unavoidable.

221
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:53,810
Are there any circumstances
more important...

222
00:12:54,580 --> 00:12:55,610
than a human life?

223
00:12:56,150 --> 00:13:00,020
Jun Ho, my blood runs through your veins.

224
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:01,790
To achieve your goals,

225
00:13:02,050 --> 00:13:04,460
you have to be ruthless enough
to throw away even people.

226
00:13:04,890 --> 00:13:06,890
Do you think the world
just hands you opportunities?

227
00:13:07,020 --> 00:13:08,860
I don't need that fortune and glory.

228
00:13:08,860 --> 00:13:10,790
Get rid of that pathetic sentimentality.

229
00:13:11,130 --> 00:13:12,730
Be ambitious,
like a son of mine should be.

230
00:13:13,330 --> 00:13:15,200
That's the only way
you'll achieve your dreams.

231
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:20,440
Your goals are to have Dream Group
and Oh Jang Mi.

232
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:22,140
Are you going to throw all of that away?

233
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:32,080
Thank you, Baek Ho.

234
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:34,080
Are you feeling any better?

235
00:13:34,690 --> 00:13:35,990
You still look pale.

236
00:13:36,890 --> 00:13:38,020
I have to pull myself together.

237
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:42,430
Right. Did you file a motion
to preserve the CCTV footage...

238
00:13:42,690 --> 00:13:44,860
at the hospital
where Seo Rin had her surgery?

239
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:49,570
Yes. But I checked the CCTV footage,
and there was nothing useful on it.

240
00:13:50,130 --> 00:13:54,100
It's a small clinic with very few cameras,
plus the video quality was awful.

241
00:13:54,870 --> 00:13:57,910
I could barely make out Seo Rin
going into the operating room.

242
00:13:58,210 --> 00:14:01,050
Was Chae Hwa Young there by any chance?

243
00:14:01,050 --> 00:14:02,050
No, she wasn't.

244
00:14:02,480 --> 00:14:04,380
I checked
Chae Hwa Young's whereabouts, too.

245
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:07,990
And her phone pinged towers in Seoul
the entire time.

246
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:10,150
I also confirmed that she was at a spa.

247
00:14:10,420 --> 00:14:14,090
Do you think Chae Hwa Young
could have gotten help?

248
00:14:14,590 --> 00:14:17,290
What if she gave her phone
to someone else to carry,

249
00:14:17,390 --> 00:14:21,000
while she herself went
to the clinic with Seo Rin?

250
00:14:22,070 --> 00:14:25,700
That's a possibility.
Or she could've used a burner phone.

251
00:14:26,400 --> 00:14:29,140
Either way,
I'll look into every possibility.

252
00:14:29,870 --> 00:14:30,980
Right now,

253
00:14:31,510 --> 00:14:33,610
none of this feels real at all.

254
00:14:34,380 --> 00:14:35,980
I feel like I'm trapped in a nightmare.

255
00:14:36,850 --> 00:14:38,450
I can't believe Seo Rin is gone
just like that.

256
00:14:42,490 --> 00:14:43,490
This must be so hard for you.

257
00:14:44,390 --> 00:14:45,620
This isn't your fault, Jang Mi.

258
00:14:46,190 --> 00:14:47,930
Chae Hwa Young is the one
who committed this crime.

259
00:14:48,290 --> 00:14:51,830
But everyone thinks I'm the one who died.

260
00:14:52,500 --> 00:14:54,030
I suddenly feel like a ghost.

261
00:14:54,160 --> 00:14:58,040
The Chairman asked you to wait
and promised to restore your name.

262
00:14:59,400 --> 00:15:00,700
So please, don't blame yourself.

263
00:15:03,540 --> 00:15:04,640
No.

264
00:15:04,640 --> 00:15:07,850
Jang Mi will stay with me forever
as Ma Seo Rin.

265
00:15:13,380 --> 00:15:15,850
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

266
00:15:15,920 --> 00:15:18,790
(Temporarily closed
due to personal reasons)

267
00:15:22,890 --> 00:15:23,890
You're just getting in?

268
00:15:24,500 --> 00:15:26,630
- How's Mom?
- Something's off with her.

269
00:15:27,900 --> 00:15:30,030
She's being unusually quiet.

270
00:15:30,800 --> 00:15:31,870
I'll go talk to her.

271
00:15:37,170 --> 00:15:38,180
Mom.

272
00:15:38,810 --> 00:15:41,310
Are you okay?
Are you feeling more like yourself?

273
00:15:52,890 --> 00:15:54,490
Chae Hwa Young did this, right?

274
00:15:56,790 --> 00:15:59,460
- Mom!
- Why did our Seo Rin have to die?

275
00:16:00,430 --> 00:16:01,870
She was perfectly healthy.

276
00:16:02,530 --> 00:16:03,570
Why would this happen so suddenly?

277
00:16:03,770 --> 00:16:04,770
Mom.

278
00:16:05,540 --> 00:16:08,570
Mom, you've come to your senses?

279
00:16:11,110 --> 00:16:12,580
That witch Chae Hwa Young...

280
00:16:13,540 --> 00:16:14,850
really...

281
00:16:15,710 --> 00:16:17,210
did kill Seo Rin, didn't she?

282
00:16:17,920 --> 00:16:19,880
- Right?
- Mom.

283
00:16:25,590 --> 00:16:27,120
I remember it all now.

284
00:16:28,430 --> 00:16:29,630
I remember that witch...

285
00:16:30,460 --> 00:16:32,000
tore you and Seo Rin...

286
00:16:32,660 --> 00:16:34,060
away from me.

287
00:16:35,100 --> 00:16:36,700
Those horrible memories...

288
00:16:38,640 --> 00:16:39,870
are all coming back to me.

289
00:16:41,270 --> 00:16:42,770
Tae Pyung!

290
00:16:49,850 --> 00:16:52,220
(My House:
Monthly Rentals near Korea University)

291
00:16:58,390 --> 00:16:59,820
You're just getting in?

292
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:02,860
What are you doing?
Are you looking at studio apartments?

293
00:17:02,990 --> 00:17:06,730
I was thinking of a place near school
and moving out.

294
00:17:07,600 --> 00:17:09,630
Are you serious about this?

295
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:13,500
I'm just so tired of all this.

296
00:17:14,140 --> 00:17:17,110
It'd be better if I just moved out
and lived on my own.

297
00:17:17,170 --> 00:17:19,340
It's the only way we'll have peace
in this family.

298
00:17:19,440 --> 00:17:20,710
You're just running away.

299
00:17:23,450 --> 00:17:27,050
- What?
- You're scared of the truth, Dad.

300
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,490
Am I wrong?

301
00:17:30,590 --> 00:17:31,690
What are you talking about?

302
00:17:31,760 --> 00:17:35,590
You're running away because you'd rather
ignore Chae Hwa Young's crimes.

303
00:17:36,630 --> 00:17:40,060
- Watch your mouth!
- Why? Did I strike a nerve?

304
00:17:40,660 --> 00:17:42,800
You're not the father I used to know.

305
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:46,370
When a man's in love,
does his brain just shut down like yours?

306
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:47,440
Why you little...

307
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:49,410
Hey!

308
00:17:50,770 --> 00:17:53,710
Don't lay a hand on my son!
What gives you the right to hit Baek Ho?

309
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:55,110
You have no right to hit him!

310
00:17:55,510 --> 00:17:57,710
Mom, calm down. I'm fine.

311
00:17:57,710 --> 00:17:59,280
A fine pair, the two of you!

312
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:01,220
That's it.
I'm leaving this house for good.

313
00:18:01,520 --> 00:18:04,460
Kang Baek Ho, don't you talk to me
like that again.

314
00:18:04,820 --> 00:18:07,990
What you think is the truth
might not be the whole story.

315
00:18:08,390 --> 00:18:10,530
Things are never that simple.

316
00:18:13,100 --> 00:18:14,100
Shut up!

317
00:18:16,300 --> 00:18:18,500
You're defending Chae Hwa Young
to the bitter end.

318
00:18:18,500 --> 00:18:20,470
When are you going to snap out of it?

319
00:18:24,370 --> 00:18:25,610
So that's what happened.

320
00:18:27,740 --> 00:18:28,750
Mom.

321
00:18:29,310 --> 00:18:30,810
Maybe I shouldn't have
told you everything.

322
00:18:32,380 --> 00:18:33,780
It's a lot to take in, isn't it?

323
00:18:34,890 --> 00:18:36,190
I had no idea...

324
00:18:37,190 --> 00:18:39,060
how much you and Seo Rin suffered...

325
00:18:40,060 --> 00:18:42,160
at the hands of that evil woman,
Chae Hwa Young.

326
00:18:43,760 --> 00:18:45,300
When you were on the brink of death,

327
00:18:45,860 --> 00:18:47,330
I couldn't even save you.

328
00:18:49,230 --> 00:18:51,870
And in the end, we lost Seo Rin...

329
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:54,240
just like that.

330
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:58,680
But, Mom,

331
00:18:59,280 --> 00:19:02,880
now that you've come back to us like this,
I'm so grateful.

332
00:19:03,550 --> 00:19:06,920
I'm not going to just stand by anymore.

333
00:19:07,520 --> 00:19:08,590
Chae Hwa Young.

334
00:19:09,750 --> 00:19:11,590
I'll make sure
you suffer the exact same way.

335
00:19:11,860 --> 00:19:12,860
Mom.

336
00:19:13,520 --> 00:19:16,530
- But you'll be endangering yourself.
- No.

337
00:19:17,490 --> 00:19:19,530
From now on, I will protect my children.

338
00:19:21,370 --> 00:19:23,030
I'm going to take down...

339
00:19:23,670 --> 00:19:25,170
that evil monster...

340
00:19:26,340 --> 00:19:28,170
who killed Seo Rin myself.

341
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:36,880
Jang Mi. Don't you worry.

342
00:19:37,380 --> 00:19:38,480
I'm strong.

343
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:42,120
I'll take it from here.

344
00:19:44,690 --> 00:19:47,120
I have a plan.

345
00:19:48,260 --> 00:19:50,290
- Mom.
- Let's keep the fact...

346
00:19:50,590 --> 00:19:53,160
that I've come to my senses a secret...

347
00:19:53,430 --> 00:19:55,630
between just the two of us, okay?

348
00:19:56,070 --> 00:19:59,040
- Why? Tae Pyung should know.
- No.

349
00:19:59,370 --> 00:20:01,170
We have to be careful for now.

350
00:20:01,740 --> 00:20:03,440
We have to make Chae Hwa Young
let her guard down.

351
00:20:03,840 --> 00:20:05,610
That's the only way to truly make her pay.

352
00:20:07,840 --> 00:20:08,880
Chae Hwa Young,

353
00:20:09,580 --> 00:20:12,950
you would never have dreamed
that I would come back like this.

354
00:20:15,090 --> 00:20:19,120
I'm going to make you pay
for everything you've done in kind.

355
00:20:40,840 --> 00:20:43,850
Why did you have to learn a secret
you weren't meant to know?

356
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:47,280
If you hadn't,
I wouldn't have had to do this to you.

357
00:20:48,590 --> 00:20:50,520
After raising you for 30 years,

358
00:20:52,420 --> 00:20:56,160
how do you think I felt
having to let you go?

359
00:20:58,060 --> 00:20:59,200
Seo Rin.

360
00:21:00,030 --> 00:21:02,000
You have to understand me.

361
00:21:02,670 --> 00:21:03,700
Okay?

362
00:21:15,150 --> 00:21:17,850
I have to get rid of all the evidence.

363
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:20,680
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

364
00:21:25,320 --> 00:21:26,320
Jang Mi?

365
00:21:27,460 --> 00:21:28,460
Oh, wait.

366
00:21:28,530 --> 00:21:31,700
Director Ma.
What a surprise to get a call from you.

367
00:21:32,100 --> 00:21:33,100
I'm happy you called.

368
00:21:34,360 --> 00:21:36,030
So you're not even sure of my name,
Jun Ho?

369
00:21:36,670 --> 00:21:39,770
That's right. Thanks to you,
I have two names now.

370
00:21:40,070 --> 00:21:42,670
- Oh Jang Mi and Ma Seo Rin.
- No, that's not it.

371
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:45,140
Ma Seo Rin has always had just one name.

372
00:21:45,340 --> 00:21:46,480
Ma Seo Rin.

373
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:48,880
- Don't get them confused.
- Shut up.

374
00:21:49,210 --> 00:21:51,110
How could you corner me like this?

375
00:21:51,110 --> 00:21:52,920
You're Chae Hwa Young's son, after all.

376
00:21:55,120 --> 00:21:56,220
You're kind of scaring me.

377
00:21:56,290 --> 00:21:58,920
I didn't call to trade jokes with you.

378
00:21:59,660 --> 00:22:02,190
Let's meet right now.
Come to the cafe at the main intersection.

379
00:22:02,390 --> 00:22:03,890
Is this your way of asking me out?

380
00:22:05,300 --> 00:22:07,300
Fine by me. I'll be there in ten.

381
00:22:08,170 --> 00:22:09,170
See you then.

382
00:22:19,240 --> 00:22:20,510
Kang Jun Ho.

383
00:22:21,980 --> 00:22:23,950
So he's Chae Hwa Young's son.

384
00:22:36,260 --> 00:22:38,060
It's been so long
since I've driven anything.

385
00:22:38,930 --> 00:22:40,400
I wonder if I'm still any good.

386
00:22:54,580 --> 00:22:56,380
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

387
00:23:00,080 --> 00:23:01,350
An eye for an eye.

388
00:23:02,120 --> 00:23:04,450
Chae Hwa Young, brace yourself.

389
00:23:05,090 --> 00:23:07,220
You'll see what becomes of your son.

390
00:23:07,890 --> 00:23:09,430
The pain I suffered...

391
00:23:10,390 --> 00:23:12,160
is what you're about to feel.

392
00:23:17,330 --> 00:23:21,270
Jun Ho, why did you switch
my name to Ma Seo Rin?

393
00:23:21,910 --> 00:23:23,970
How could you make Seo Rin, who died,
into Oh Jang Mi...

394
00:23:24,270 --> 00:23:26,810
and declare me, who's perfectly alive,
to be dead?

395
00:23:27,540 --> 00:23:30,250
What kind of twisted mind
comes up with an idea like that?

396
00:23:30,650 --> 00:23:32,750
When you're in love,
you don't even have to try hard.

397
00:23:34,080 --> 00:23:35,090
You're insane.

398
00:23:35,750 --> 00:23:38,460
No, you're actually scaring me, Jun Ho.

399
00:23:39,090 --> 00:23:41,160
I can't believe you'd mistake
that terrifying obsession for love.

400
00:23:41,160 --> 00:23:42,730
Don't you think you should get some help?

401
00:23:43,530 --> 00:23:44,530
You're right.

402
00:23:45,200 --> 00:23:47,000
I'm terminally ill with love.

403
00:23:47,630 --> 00:23:50,270
And the only one who can cure me
is you, Ma Seo Rin.

404
00:23:50,470 --> 00:23:51,740
My name is Oh Jang Mi.

405
00:23:52,370 --> 00:23:53,770
Stop it. You're creeping me out.

406
00:23:54,670 --> 00:23:55,670
How much...

407
00:23:56,240 --> 00:23:58,240
do I have to humiliate you...

408
00:23:58,740 --> 00:24:01,850
- before you'll finally stop?
- I'll stop at nothing to get what I want.

409
00:24:02,710 --> 00:24:04,080
So just give up on Baek Ho.

410
00:24:04,950 --> 00:24:07,650
I can make you much happier
than Baek Ho ever could, Seo Rin.

411
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:08,920
Stop it!

412
00:24:10,490 --> 00:24:12,290
Your obsession is repulsive.

413
00:24:12,560 --> 00:24:14,990
Kang Jun Ho. Let me be perfectly clear.

414
00:24:15,590 --> 00:24:18,160
I will never love you,
not in this life or the next.

415
00:24:18,460 --> 00:24:20,560
I never have before,

416
00:24:21,430 --> 00:24:22,930
and I never will.

417
00:24:24,470 --> 00:24:25,470
No.

418
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:28,570
You will marry me, Seo Rin.

419
00:24:29,170 --> 00:24:31,840
Our wedding was called off
when you went back to being Oh Jang Mi.

420
00:24:33,140 --> 00:24:35,750
But now that you're Ma Seo Rin again,
it's back on.

421
00:24:36,710 --> 00:24:37,750
Director Ma Seo Rin.

422
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:41,590
You won't get your way.

423
00:24:42,550 --> 00:24:44,020
Thank you, Kang Jun Ho,

424
00:24:44,720 --> 00:24:47,890
for getting rid of the last shred
of human pity I had for you.

425
00:24:52,330 --> 00:24:54,030
I'm not done talking.

426
00:24:55,570 --> 00:24:56,900
I have nothing more to say.

427
00:25:01,970 --> 00:25:02,970
Mom?

428
00:25:04,070 --> 00:25:05,080
Kang Jun Ho.

429
00:25:05,640 --> 00:25:07,140
I remember your face now.

430
00:25:07,740 --> 00:25:09,410
Chae Hwa Young's son, Kang Jun Ho.

431
00:25:10,310 --> 00:25:11,920
I'm going to kill you.

432
00:25:12,650 --> 00:25:15,250
You're about to find out
what it's like to die,

433
00:25:16,050 --> 00:25:17,420
just like my daughter Seo Rin did.

434
00:25:18,320 --> 00:25:20,120
Chae Hwa Young,
you're about to find out...

435
00:25:20,460 --> 00:25:22,790
what it feels like to lose a child.

436
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:27,430
I will rip your son to shreds...

437
00:25:27,960 --> 00:25:30,170
until he's unrecognizable.

438
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:32,640
In unimaginable agony,

439
00:25:33,040 --> 00:25:34,970
he will die regretting
that he was ever born your son.

440
00:25:35,270 --> 00:25:38,440
That's the death I'm going to give him.
Chae Hwa Young!

441
00:25:39,410 --> 00:25:41,880
You're going to lose
what's most precious to you, too!

442
00:25:47,650 --> 00:25:49,790
Mom, don't do this.

443
00:25:50,290 --> 00:25:52,360
This just makes you no better
than Chae Hwa Young.

444
00:25:57,430 --> 00:25:58,460
Jang Mi.

445
00:26:05,740 --> 00:26:07,670
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

446
00:26:14,280 --> 00:26:15,810
Seo Rin?

447
00:26:17,250 --> 00:26:18,250
Are you okay?

448
00:26:19,080 --> 00:26:20,650
Are you going to keep calling me Seo Rin?

449
00:26:21,350 --> 00:26:22,690
I'm Oh Jang Mi.

450
00:26:23,120 --> 00:26:25,560
The Oh Jang Mi who's married
to your brother, Baek Ho.

451
00:26:27,790 --> 00:26:28,790
Seo Rin.

452
00:26:29,590 --> 00:26:32,600
(Suk Hee's Side Dishes)

453
00:26:33,130 --> 00:26:37,730
Jang Mi,
I guess I lost my mind for a second there.

454
00:26:38,700 --> 00:26:39,740
I almost...

455
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:42,070
got you hurt, too.

456
00:26:42,370 --> 00:26:46,510
All I could think about
making Chae Hwa Young suffer deeply.

457
00:26:46,810 --> 00:26:48,310
I know how you feel, Mom.

458
00:26:49,180 --> 00:26:50,250
But, Mom,

459
00:26:52,220 --> 00:26:53,880
if we act just like Chae Hwa Young,

460
00:26:54,150 --> 00:26:56,120
we'll become monsters like her.

461
00:26:56,290 --> 00:26:58,560
And you'll end up getting hurt, Mom.

462
00:26:58,790 --> 00:27:01,560
I guess I got carried away.

463
00:27:02,190 --> 00:27:04,290
Mom, promise me.

464
00:27:04,730 --> 00:27:07,600
Promise you won't seek such reckless
and dangerous revenge again.

465
00:27:08,260 --> 00:27:11,200
I'm so scared.
If I lose you too, what will I do?

466
00:27:11,940 --> 00:27:16,740
I won't do anything dangerous...

467
00:27:16,740 --> 00:27:17,970
that would make you worry.

468
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:20,880
Okay, I promise.

469
00:27:56,110 --> 00:27:57,710
(The First Man)

470
00:27:57,850 --> 00:28:01,320
I think it's time
to let Jun Ho in on everything.

471
00:28:01,650 --> 00:28:05,590
This is the shell company
we're going to use...

472
00:28:05,990 --> 00:28:07,220
to swallow Dream Group whole.

473
00:28:07,220 --> 00:28:10,990
Who was there for you when you were
devastated by your infertility diagnosis?

474
00:28:11,190 --> 00:28:13,860
Does that mean I'm not your son?

475
00:28:14,330 --> 00:28:15,330
Baek Ho.

476
00:28:15,330 --> 00:28:19,900
I have to find out why
Chae Hwa Young had to kill Seo Rin.

477
00:28:20,100 --> 00:28:23,440
The horrible secret
that made her silence Seo Rin.

478
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:27,640
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
